  "data": {
    "description": "<p>You may use this skill if your subclass is Knight, Hero, or Wuxia.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>You can only target people other than yourself who are willing with this skill. When you use \"Protect\" on the target, it becomes [Range: 1 Sq] and you will not become [Post-Action]. This can be used while [Post-Action]. This effect lasts until the end of the scenario.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>A special skill in which one swears an oath of protection over one's own sword. As long as I hold this oath, I will never let any blade reach me.</p>",
